cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper deals with data association problems in computer vision, specifically in the context of multi-object tracking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning features for network-flow-based data association, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of network flow formulations and optimization techniques could also place it in cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
